    <div id="text">
        <p>The Sentinel Project is designed to help the Lawrenceville School keep track of its students after hours. The system is running 24 hours a day, and used by the entire student body and faculty of the Lawrenceville School.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="tech"> <span>Tech Used</span>
